<![CDATA[<div><font face="arial">Hi&nbsp;{!Lead.FirstName},</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Welcome to MBO Partners! I have just activated your account so you’re ready to get started on your assignment. Below is some important information every “MBO Staff” Associate working with McAfee should know. Please keep this email handy so that you can refer back to it as needed.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>Entering Your Time and Client-Billable Expenses</b></font></div><div><font face="arial">As you work, you are responsible for recording your time through your online MBO Business Center (<a href="http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Staff_Time_and_Expense_Entry_Instructions.pdf">instructions</a>, <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">page&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(51, 204, 0);">Adjust this link (and the one below) if necessary.</span></font><span style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;1). </span><u style="font-family: arial;"><b>Be sure to submit your entries by close of business each Monday for the previous week’s work</b></u><span style="font-family: arial;">.&nbsp;</span></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you incur expenses that can be billed back to McAfee, submit them through your MBO Business Center as well (<a href="http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Staff_Time_and_Expense_Entry_Instructions.pdf">instructions</a>, pages 2 and 3).</font></div><div><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Payment Timing</b></font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Once you begin your assignment, MBO direct-deposits your payments weekly (one week in arrears). Please note that your first payments may be via a paper check.</font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Payment Timing</b></font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Once you begin your assignment, MBO direct-deposits your payments weekly (two weeks in arrears). Please note that your first payments may be via a paper check.&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(51, 204, 0);">Select the appropriate paragraph(s) and delete the other(s) (and this comment).</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>Ongoing Support</b></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you have any questions or concerns about your engagement with McAfee, I’m here to help. As an MBO Staff Associate, you enjoy unlimited phone and email support from MBO while you work on your client assignments.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Again, welcome to MBO! It has been a pleasure working with you, and I appreciate your patience during the on-boarding process. On behalf of everyone here, I sincerely hope that we offer a positive experience as you work on your project assignment.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Best regards,</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">{!Lead.rs_BM__c}</font></div><div><font face="arial">Business Manager</font></div><div><font face="arial">703-793-<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">XXXX</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div>]]></td>
